<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Owner Console</title>

    <!-- Owner 전용 스타일 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/owner/owner.css" />
</head>
<body>

<div class="app" data-default-tab="<%= activeTab %>">
    <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar__brand">
            <div class="brand__logo">
                <img src="/static/owner/logo.png" alt="K&N Logo" />
            </div>
            <div class="brand__text">
                <div class="brand__title">Owner Console</div>
                <div class="brand__sub">Server Dashboard</div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <nav class="nav">
            <button class="nav__item" data-tab="dashboard">
                <span class="nav__label">서버 상태</span>
            </button>

            <button class="nav__item" data-tab="employee-sessions">
                <span class="nav__label">직원 로그인 상태</span>
            </button>

            <button class="nav__item" data-tab="api-logs">
                <span class="nav__label">API 요청</span>
            </button>

            <button class="nav__item" data-tab="error-logs">
                <span class="nav__label">에러 API</span>
            </button>
        </nav>

        <div class="sidebar__footer">
            <div class="hint">
                사이드바 클릭 시 실제 페이지 이동 없이 콘텐츠만 교체합니다.
            </div>
        </div>
    </aside>

    <section class="main">
        <header class="topbar">
            <div class="topbar__left">
                <div class="topbar__title" id="topbar-title">Dashboard</div>
                <div class="topbar__desc" id="topbar-desc">
                    서버 상태와 운영 데이터를 확인합니다.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="topbar__right">
                <div class="pill" id="server-pill">LIVE</div>
                <a
                        class="topbar__link"
                        href="/docs"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noreferrer"
                >
                    API Docs
                </a>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="content" id="owner-content">
            <div class="skeleton">
                <div class="skeleton__bar"></div>
                <div class="skeleton__bar"></div>
                <div class="skeleton__bar"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div id="owner-modal-root"></div>
</div>

<script src="/static/owner/owner.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
